name: citation-policy
description: Every Fact, Decision, and Event must cite a Source.
---

# Rule

A note of type `fact`, `decision`, or `event` MUST include at least one
entry in its `sources:` frontmatter list. The orchestrator rejects writes
that violate this. If a candidate atomic unit cannot be tied to a source,
the classifier should down-rank `fact`/`decision`/`event` and prefer
`note` or `hypothesis`.
